Package: gnome-disk-utility
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, devicekit-disks
Description: manage and configure disk drives and media
 gnome-disk-utility utilizes DeviceKit-disks to allow for easy management of
 disk drives and media.
  o Format and partition drives.
  o Mount and unmount partitions.
  o Query S.M.A.R.T. attributes.

